## 📦 **KIPANDE 1: MWANZO WA PROJECT (Foundation)**

```bash
# Create Flutter project
flutter create water_delivery_app
cd water_delivery_app

# Create root folders
mkdir lib\core
mkdir lib\config
mkdir lib\features
mkdir lib\shared
```

**Baada ya kipande hiki, una:**
```
water_delivery_app/
├── lib/
│   ├── core/
│   ├── config/
│   ├── features/
│   └── shared/
├── android/
├── ios/
└── pubspec.yaml
```

